name: Arch USD Div. Yield

description.en: Arch USD Diversified Yield is an ERC-20 token product from Arch Finance (DeFi Asset Management). The token is comprised of a selection of strategies that generate yield on USD-denominated stablecoins. The allocation of assets is based on the relative total value locked (TVL) across strategies on major yield-farming protocols.
